Apply profile to device

Usage: wheelctl profile apply [OPTIONS] <DEVICE> <PROFILE>

Arguments:
  <DEVICE>   Device ID or name
  <PROFILE>  Profile path or ID

Options:
      --json             Output in JSON format for machine parsing
      --skip-validation  Skip validation
  -v, --verbose...       Verbose logging
  -h, --help             Print help
